Brighten up your day with this colourful tomato salad.
Share to Facebook Share to Twitter Email Print
1 medium green or red tomato, cut into eight
3 baby or cherry bocconcini cheese, about 60g total, cut or torn
2 teaspoon fresh basil, leaves only (fresh basil leaves and other fresh herbs
1 Place all the tomatoes on a plate.
2 If using baby bocconcini cheese then slice into thin slices, leave cherry
3 Sprinkle over black pepper, basil leaves and balsamic vinegar.
This salad makes an excellent side dish to your lean protein of choice.
